 Collectors.toMap()

 Ek line me:

 List → Map convert karna ho, to Collectors.toMap() use karte hain.

 Sabse Pehle Problem

 Maan lo tumhare paas Employees ki List hai.

 101  Rahul
 102  Amit
 103  Neha
 104  Riya

 Ab manager bolta hai:

 "Mujhe List nahi chahiye.
 Mujhe Employee ID se direct Employee chahiye."

 Agar List rahegi to search karna padega.

 for(Employee e : employees){
     if(e.getId()==103){
         return e;
     }
 }

 Time lagta hai.

 Lekin agar Map ho

 101 → Rahul
 102 → Amit
 103 → Neha
 104 → Riya

 To

 map.get(103);

 Bas.

 O(1) lookup.

 Isi liye toMap() bana.

 Real Life Analogy

 School Register

 List

 Roll No    Name

 1          Rahul
 2          Amit
 3          Neha
 4          Riya

 Principal bolta hai

 "Roll Number batao."

 Teacher ko pura register dekhna padega.

 Lekin agar

 1 → Rahul

 2 → Amit

 3 → Neha

 4 → Riya

 To direct mil jayega.

 Ye hi toMap() hai.

 Syntax
 Collectors.toMap(
     keyMapper,
     valueMapper
 )

 Yaad rakhna:

 Key kis se banegi?

 ↓

 Value kya hogi?